        or Name = 'Linda'
        or Name = 'Jessica'
        or Name = 'Ashley'
        or Name='Jennifer'
    group by Name, Year
    order by Year

import matplotlib
%matplotlib inline

df = dataframe().toPandas()
names_over_year = df.pivot("Year", "Name", "Count")
names_over_year.plot()
fig = matplotlib.pyplot.gcf()
